0.4.0
Can now handle shoulda tests/focused tests. Run a focused should
by specifying a line anywhere inside of the should. Run a focused
context by specifying the line on which the context starts.

0.2.0
FocusedTest.run and FocusedTest.new now take a splatted array.

0.1.1
FocusedTest#parse properly uses args local variable instead of using ARGV.

